1
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,000
Ling.

2
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,040
About Hanxing,

3
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,760
don't be too sad.

4
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,820
How do you know about Hanxing?

5
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,800
In the whole palace, the one who can make you sad,

6
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,460
or put you in a difficult spot,

7
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,400
is only her.

8
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:19,920
You aren't jealous of Hanxing, are you?

9
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:20,600
Yes.

10
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:25,050
You just can't treat others better than you treat me.

11
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,680
What are you laughing at?

12
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,690
I want to let Hanxing go.

13
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,660
You can't hurt her.

14
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,079
Okay.

15
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:42,120
Leave the Ghost Mask matter

16
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:42,720
to me.

17
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,450
I will investigate.

18
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,240
Okay.

19
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:48,200
You should get some rest.

20
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,440
I'll sleep on the daybed.

21
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:52,840
No.

22
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,280
Ling.

23
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,960
May I be bold and get close to you tonight?

24
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:11,640
Fine.

25
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,300
Let's indulge just this once.

26
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:17,920
Li Yunxi.

27
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,690
We are husband and wife, after all.

28
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,220
You have been exposed.

29
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,040
I don't know what you're talking about.

30
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:13,680
You disguised yourselves as the Xuanniao Tribe

31
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,280
to assassinate the Emperor.

32
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,360
I may have forged it,

33
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,290
but I hope it stops you in time, Father.

34
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,680
Since you know the truth,

35
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,360
you ought to know

36
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,760
how your mother and brother

37
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,880
met their ends.

38
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:29,920
Two years ago,

39
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,080
the secret order to kill Mother and Brother,

40
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,080
who gave it to you?

41
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,159
It is like the snipe and the clam fighting,

42
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,520
and the fisherman catching both.

43
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:39,040
That person is hiding in the shadows.

44
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,570
What is his true intention?

45
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,120
If you insist on acting this way,

46
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,880
what will become of the loyal Xiao Army

47
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,010
and its reputation?

48
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,000
Loyal?

49
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,800
Loyal?

50
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,020
What is the use of loyalty?

51
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,400
I,

52
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,440
Xiao Rushan,

53
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,280
guarded the Li family's empire,

54
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:03,540
but couldn't protect my own wife and son.

55
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,160
I...

56
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,280
But blind revenge like this

57
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,760
will only breed more hatred.

58
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,320
Fine.

59
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,680
Since you are so devoted to the Emperor,

60
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,930
from this day forth,

61
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,040
I disown you as my daughter.

62
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,480
You protect your husband,

63
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,940
and I will take my revenge.

64
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,490
We go our separate ways.

65
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:27,960
Father.

66
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,850
Please reconsider.

67
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:31,920
Get out!

68
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,400
I never want to see you again.

69
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,740
Ghost Face was once entangled in my whip,

70
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,100
so his arm must be injured.

71
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,320
Get out!

72
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,940
But Father's arm showed no reaction.

73
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:08,400
Father definitely isn't Ghost Face.

74
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:09,530
Then who could it be?

75
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,680
You're pregnant.

76
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,940
Why are you still so reckless?

77
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,880
Few people know I'm pregnant.

78
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,080
Could it be...

79
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,880
Do you have a secret?

80
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,680
Everyone has their own secrets.

81
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,159
Don't you?

82
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,440
It's not him.

83
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,330
Thank goodness.

84
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,460
What is wrong with you?

85
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:04,200
I've been paranoid lately.

86
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,000
Sorry.

87
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,440
Back then, around this time,

88
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,760
you'd always treat me to a drink.

89
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:11,200
We would

90
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,330
drink until we dropped.

91
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,360
Prince Qi.

92
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,640
I have no romantic feelings for you.

93
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,250
I only see you

94
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,240
as a brother-in-arms.

95
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,100
I'll take my leave.

96
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,010
Why are you back so late?

97
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,960
I failed to bring back the assassin.

98
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,000
Are you hurt?

99
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,090
Are you okay?

100
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,540
You scared me to death.

101
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,680
Perhaps,

102
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:14,290
letting Father's fate unfold as in the previous life

103
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,560
is the best outcome.

104
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,360
I'm fine.

105
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,400
But

106
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,440
I found this

107
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,050
on the assassin.

108
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,490
The Xuanniao Tribe.

109
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:31,960
Wait,

110
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,679
the tail feathers are slightly different.

111
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,360
It's a fake.

112
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:46,450
What is going on?

113
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,320
Why the big commotion?

114
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,320
His Majesty stayed at Jile Hall last night.

115
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,920
Early this morning, he ordered Lord Su

116
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:54,380
to send over many rewards.

117
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:58,060
There are assassins hiding in the Xiao Army.

118
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,000
His Majesty isn't investigating.

119
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,060
Instead, he's favoring the Empress.

120
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:02,960
My Lady,

121
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:04,600
what do you plan to do?

122
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,970
I absolutely cannot

123
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,760
let the Empress's child be born.

124
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,840
Hanxing.

125
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,040
I am Ruyan.

126
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:32,370
I'm taking Hanxing's place to serve you, Your Highness.

127
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,210
What incense is burning today?

128
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,640
It smells different.

129
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,720
It's your favorite lily scent.

130
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:47,000
I saw the autumn osmanthus is excellent,

131
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,520
so I added some.

132
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,280
No wonder it warms my heart.

133
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,010
That was thoughtful of you.

134
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,200
You may leave.

135
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,400
I shall take my leave.

136
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:09,560
Consort Xue.

137
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,760
The Empress loves this incense.

138
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,760
She asked me to burn it day and night.

139
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:17,120
This incense is laced with plenty of musk.

140
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:21,040
She's been breathing it in for ten days.

141
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,560
How could the Empress's baby

142
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:24,240
be completely unharmed?

143
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,770
Why isn't the Empress here?

144
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:34,720
Consort Xue.

145
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:37,800
The Empress asks that you wait here.

146
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:00,440
Please take a seat, Your Highness.

147
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,900
Who gave you the audacity?

148
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,200
How dare you block me?

149
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:03,840
It was me.

150
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,360
Empress,

151
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:10,570
what is the meaning of this?

152
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:12,340
It's called giving you a taste

153
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:14,240
of your own medicine.

154
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,160
So you know.

155
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:20,160
Thanks to Ruyan.

156
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:22,800
Consort Xue, I didn't.

157
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,720
How dare you betray me!

158
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,970
Your Highness, I didn't say anything.

159
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,360
You knew there was a problem with this incense,

160
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:34,160
yet you smelled it day and night.

161
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,000
I smelled it for a moment,

162
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:38,530
and felt discomfort in my abdomen.

163
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:41,540
You smelled it but had no reaction at all.

164
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:45,440
You are not pregnant at all.

165
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:49,980
What are you making a scene about now?

166
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,520
Your Majesty.

167
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,400
Your Majesty.

168
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:58,080
The Empress faked a pregnancy to vie for favor.

169
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:00,610
This is the crime of deceiving the sovereign.

170
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,820
I already know about this.

171
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,240
It is not the Empress's fault.

172
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:10,080
It was the Imperial Physician's misdiagnosis.

173
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:10,840
What?

174
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,660
I will deal with the Imperial Physician myself.

175
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,130
What act are you putting on now?

176
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:21,260
She is pregnant and smelled musk.

177
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,160
Pregnant.
